Command:
curl -X PUT "http://localhost:3000/customer/auth/review/1?review=Great%20book!" -b cookies.txt

Output:
{"message":"Review successfully added/updated"}

Note: Requires authentication (login first and save cookies with -c cookies.txt, then use -b cookies.txt)

---

Verification Command:
curl http://localhost:3000/review/1

Output:
{
    "john": "Great book!"
}

Note: The review is stored with the username as the key, allowing multiple users to review the same book.
